episodes.title: DOOMSDAY, SEX GODDESS, CULT MURDERING MOM
episodes.description: Have you heard of the doomsday mom?  Join Lav and Staci while they discuss Lori Vallow Daybell, who is accused along with her husband Chad Daybell, was sentenced to life without parole after an Idaho jury found her guilty in May on all charges for her role in the deaths of her 16-year-old daughter, Tylee Ryan; her 7-year-old adopted son, Joshua "JJ" Vallow.  To make this story even more heartbreaking and bizarre. This couple who was a cult leader and his sex goddess bride also face other charges related to the mysterious deaths of both of their former spouses.   IG: Early_on.Wednesday Email: Earlyonwed@gmail.com Facebook: Early on Wednesday Podcast (group) STACI: witch.with.all.the.gifts666 Lav: early.on.wednesday_Lav
